name: R4B-SpecimenDefinition-R5-SpecimenDefinition
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B SpecimenDefinition into FHIR R5

target.comment: R4B `SpecimenDefinition` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.collection` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.collection`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.contained` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.contained`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.id`

element.display: Business identifier of a kind of specimen

target.comment: R4B `SpecimenDefinition.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.identifier`

target.comment: R4B `SpecimenDefinition.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.implicitRules`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.language` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.language` - language made the binding required (from Preferred) for http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-languages|5.0.0
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.meta` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.meta`

R4B `SpecimenDefinition.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`
R4B `SpecimenDefinition.patientPreparation` maps as Equivalent to R5 `SpecimenDefinition.patientPreparation`
